ygData.messageBody:
I'll be glad to help you! Gimme a tell when you are on. Like Minkin said -
it's not hard. You could easily buy one in Beholder, prolly join a group
there and get one in loots, or we can go kill some minos and get em for
free. How many songs does your bard have?

Sylly Songsynger
<Spirit of the Moon>
Bard of the 33rd song
somewhere on Innoruuk
